file_content.text: Not like this...
It's over.
You can't win. You know that.
I choose my own fate.
Commander, the omnicannon's back online!
Good. I'm done here. Arcann's finished.
I never doubted you.
Gault and Vette ran into some trouble, but we managed.
Torian and Vette ran into some trouble, but we managed.
Torian and Gault ran into some trouble, but we managed.
We're at the shuttle. I can't get ahold of Senya. The ship is falling apart.
You'll need to find another way back to the Gravestone.
Typical. Now that the dirty work's done, I'm left to rot.
Sure. Leave the hero behind.
I'm open to suggestions.
I hope you have a plan.
I just defeated the Emperor of Zakuul. I won't die now.
Dying would ruin my victory.
You will wait for me. That's an order.
Nobody leaves until I'm there!
There's a wing of patrol ships not far from the bridge.
You're our commander--we'd never leave you behind.
Respectfully, Commander, you won't make it.
I'll target the fleet--buy you as much time as I can.
It's over, Arcann. Surrender. Now.
I don't want to kill you.
Your reign is over, "Emperor."
At last. [Kill Arcann]
